name: PEPECASH | Series 1
description:
PEPECASH is a Series 1, Card 11 of the iconic Rare Pepe Wallet set, but it's much more than that being an antique NFT giving it historic value.

This legendary collection of NFTs was minted on Counterparty (XCP) from 2016-18 for basically no reason, long before the barrage of normie NFTs seen today. Many XCP wallets have been lost over the years, thus circulation often lower than issuance.



View contents of NFT by expanding Properties Below and at Emblem.Finance 👇

[View this NFT on Emblem.Finance](https://emblem.finance/nft?id=48604554603993941)
